 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Tengentsu&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Reduces next damage taken by 10%. +10 Kenki, 200 potency regen and 10% mit for 9s if hit. 4s duration, 15s CD.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
